> Has anyone EVER snapped one? I hope not.

I have seen them snapped, but always in cases of abuse in Baja Bugs.

You might be able to tell the original installation direction of used bars
by examining the splines.  One face of each spline has been in continuous
contact with the mating spline while the other has not.

